data.description: Welcome to your dream property! This stunning property is now available and ready to become your oasis. Situated on a corner lot, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style. With its spacious floor plan, 4 bedrooms, and 2 baths, this home provides ample space for you to relax and make lasting memories. As you enter the home, you'll be greeted by new flooring and trim work throughout, adding a touch of elegance to every room. The open layout seamlessly connects the living areas, creating an inviting atmosphere for entertaining guests or spending quality time with loved ones. The abundance of natural light that filters through the large windows enhances the warm and welcoming ambiance. The master bedroom is a true retreat, offering privacy and tranquility after a long day. With its generous size, it provides ample space for all your furniture needs. You'll also appreciate the convenience of having an en-suite bathroom, ensuring your utmost comfort and convenience. The interior and exterior of this home has been freshly painted, providing a clean and modern look that will surely impress your visitors. The new trim further enhances the overall appeal while highlighting the architectural details of the home. The corner lot offers additional privacy and space for outdoor activities or landscaping projects. Parking will never be an issue with 6+ dedicated parking spaces available for you and your guests. Whether you have multiple vehicles or enjoy hosting gatherings, you'll have plenty of room to accommodate everyone. Located in Sarasota, Florida, this property offers proximity to a wide range of amenities. Enjoy easy access to shopping centers, restaurants, schools, parks, Downtown Sarasota, UTC and more. Sarasota's renowned beaches are just a short drive away, allowing you to soak up the sun and enjoy the coastal lifestyle whenever you desire. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a beautiful home and oversized property in one of Sarasota's most sought-after neighborhoods. With its impeccable features and prime location, 609 Houle Avenue is truly a gem. Add your personal touches and make this house your home. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and prepare to fall in love with this remarkable property.
